// 2.8 | 2022-03-04 | mmcc | STRY0114453 - Org Hierarchy Full Screen- Tree Node- Avatar Control- Popover Panel
//											Updated loadPhotoInfo() to use sys_user; Added getConnectEnabled();
//											in loadProfileInfo() added mobilePhone, contactPageHref, photo, emailSubject, buttonText and icons;
//											Changed phone to businessPhone
// 2.8 | 2022-03-10 | mmcc | STRY0114453 - Org Hierarchy Full Screen- Tree Node- Avatar Control- Popover Panel
//											Cleaned up getConnectEnabled(); Added object messages; 
//											Removed emailSubject and buttonText as they will added to the messages object
